					<dd class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
						<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-5708">
<p>I marinate scallops in a bit of REALLY GOOD teriyaki sauce and lemon for a few hours, then blot dry with paper towel and whiz them through a very hot saute pan (peanut oil) to brown on each side.  The teriyaki marinade makes a bit of a sauce. Delicious.</p>
